subject: HISTORY
text: Give the century, B.C. or A.D., of each of the following, indicate who or what each was, and say why each is important in history: The Black Death, Hernando Cortes, Demosthenes, the Secret Treaty of Dover, Edward the Confessor, Bishop Kennedy, the Battle of Pharsalia, the British North America Act, William Caxton, Walpole’s Excise Bill.
